snippet.title: HITMAN - The Complete 1st season Steel Book Edition - Trailer
snippet.description:
The perfect man for the mission and the only one who guarantees you mind-blowing (literally) challenges with zero-evidence left behind. HITMAN: The Complete First Season - Available now on PlayStation 4, XBOX ONE & PC
